Setup
-----

In order to preview and deploy:
  Requirements:
  - Ruby 1.9.3

  gem install bundler
  bundle install

To just write a post, see below

New post
--------

If you have rake:
  rake new_post["title"]

Otherwise create a file in source/_posts with the name:

year-month-day-title.markdown (see other files in the folder)

add it and git push.

Generate and Preview
--------------------

If you have rake:
 rake generate
 rake preview

 visit http://localhost:4000/dsrg

Deploy
------

Only one person should be doing this.  Currently it's neha, to
amsterdam.  If this changes, change Rakefile.

 rake generate
 rake deploy